A '''rigora''' was a type of duel practiced by the [[Phosphura Belt Pirates]] as a means of solving internal disputes. As dictated by the [[Rules of the Blade]], rigoras could be declared if a [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] felt his or her name, ship, or crew had been dishonored. Some rigoras were fought till one fell unconscious to the ground while others were fought to the death depending on the nature of the grievance. Energy weapons were allowed, but explosives were considered poor conduct.<ref name="Zirtran's Anchor (article)">{{JournalCite|5|Zirtran's Anchor (article)}}</ref>

There were several types of rigora such as the [[just rigora]], the [[honor rigora]], and the [[oath rigora]].<ref name="Zirtran's Anchor (article)" />

